# Web3 Payment App Starter

This is the starter project used in the YouTube series.

## Setup

### 1. Clone repo
git clone <repo-url>

### 2. Install dependencies
cd client && npm install  
cd ../backend && npm install  

### 3. Run project
# backend
npm run dev

# frontend
npm run dev

## What’s included
- React frontend
- Express backend
- Base structure for Web3 auth (Privy)